All UK Medical students and interim FY1s – what are your thoughts on volunteering during #covid19? Do you feel ready?
Let us know via the @CovidReady study by completing this questionnaire – https://t.co/ANvqNvy1LG #medstudentcovid #medstudenttwitter #CovidReadyStudy
